WEBVTT

00:04.124 --> 00:06.753
Okay, this is threaded.
Here, you take this.

00:06.754 --> 00:07.623
Okay.

00:07.624 --> 00:09.043
I got this.
You take this.

00:09.044 --> 00:10.463
- Okay.
- Wait a minute.

00:10.464 --> 00:11.463
- Oh, God.
- Okay.

00:11.464 --> 00:12.503
All right, now...

00:12.504 --> 00:13.503
click it in.

00:13.504 --> 00:14.543
Okay, push it.

00:14.544 --> 00:15.543
(straining): I am pushing.

00:15.544 --> 00:16.543
No, push it down.

00:16.544 --> 00:18.575
I am...
pushing it down!

00:18.576 --> 00:20.155
- Okay, I think that's it.
- (seat belt clicks)

00:20.156 --> 00:21.745
- (groans) Okay.
- Okay.

00:21.746 --> 00:22.945
- Let me get mine in.
- Okay.

00:22.946 --> 00:24.745
And tighten her up.

00:24.746 --> 00:25.745
- Good.
- (panting): Like that.

00:25.746 --> 00:27.035
- All right, let me just take...
- Yeah.

00:27.036 --> 00:28.695
- Take up the slack. (groans)
- Okay.

00:28.696 --> 00:31.865
(screams)
You're cutting me in half!

00:31.866 --> 00:32.945
I'm gonna release my sides!

00:32.946 --> 00:34.985
- Ow! Oh.
- Oh.

00:34.986 --> 00:36.325
Oh, Mol!

00:36.326 --> 00:38.326
(panting)

00:41.036 --> 00:43.075
Honey...

00:43.076 --> 00:46.365
can we please just take
this thing to the fire station

00:46.366 --> 00:49.115
where they will
install it for free?

00:49.116 --> 00:51.905
Yeah, maybe they'll do it
for you shirtless, too.

00:51.906 --> 00:53.985
(chuckles) Don't worry.

00:53.986 --> 00:56.905
You're still my first
responder of choice.

00:56.906 --> 00:57.946
Thank you.

00:59.576 --> 01:01.325
You believe it?

01:01.326 --> 01:03.615
Three weeks, we're gonna
have a baby in this thing.

01:03.616 --> 01:05.035
You're gonna be a mom.

01:05.036 --> 01:06.945
You're gonna be a dad.

01:06.946 --> 01:07.945
Mama.

01:07.946 --> 01:09.945
(foreign accent): Papa.

01:09.946 --> 01:11.115
(chuckles)

01:11.116 --> 01:12.945
Okay, well, let's get
this damn car seat in

01:12.946 --> 01:15.985
so Mom and Dad aren't gonna
have to walk baby six miles home

01:15.986 --> 01:18.035
from the hospital.

01:18.036 --> 01:19.905
You know what?

01:19.906 --> 01:23.785
You have been working
really hard on this.

01:23.786 --> 01:25.535
Why don't you just...

01:25.536 --> 01:27.285
go take a nap or something,

01:27.286 --> 01:29.745
and I'll, I'll give
this another shot.

01:29.746 --> 01:31.400
You want to try
to do this alone?

01:33.812 --> 01:35.092
(whispering):
Just go take a nap.

01:37.022 --> 01:39.441
Okay, but don't take it
to Firehouse Seven...

01:39.442 --> 01:40.732
those guys know me.

01:46.362 --> 01:49.731
